14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 5029A of Title 63, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 A. There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving
19 fund for the Oklahoma Health Care Authority to be designated the
20 "Intergenerational Education Revolving Fund". The fund shall be a
21 continuing fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall
22 consist of all monies directed for deposit to the fund by law. All
23 monies accruing to the credit of said fund are hereby appropriated
24 and may be budgeted and expended by the Oklahoma Health Care
